exports[`email templates render exactly (localization guard) > feedback ack (C9a) 1`] = `
{
  "html": "<!doctype html>
<html><body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#FBFAF7;">
<div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;color:#15243B;">
  <div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:24px;">Get Camino <span style="color:#8A9BB0;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;">— your road to Spain</span></div>
  <p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">Thanks — your message reached me.</p><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">Get Camino is built and answered by one person, so a reply usually takes about four to five days. If something is time-sensitive, your consulate's appointment page (cita previa) is the fastest route — I can't help with urgent cases.</p><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">In the meantime, these might already have your answer:</p><div style="margin:24px 0;"><a href="https://getcamino.app/questions" style="display:inline-block;background:#2B5AA3;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:12px 22px;border-radius:8px;">Common questions</a></div><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;"><a href="https://getcamino.app/changelog" style="color:#2B5AA3;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">See what's changed lately →</a></p>
  <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #E8E4DC;margin:32px 0 16px;">
  <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#8A9BB0;">
    
    <br>Guidance only — not legal or tax advice.
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>",
  "subject": "We got your message — Get Camino",
  "text": "Thanks — your message reached me.

Get Camino is built and answered by one person, so a reply usually takes about four to five days. If something is time-sensitive, your consulate's appointment page (cita previa) is the fastest route — I can't help with urgent cases.

In the meantime, these might already have your answer:
Common questions: https://getcamino.app/questions
What's changed lately: https://getcamino.app/changelog",
}
`;

