  </div>
</div>
</body></html>",
  "subject": "Your Spain roadmap is waiting — a few questions to go",
  "text": "Hola — Lola here.

You started telling me about your move to Spain. A few more answers and I can lay out your full roadmap.

Pick up where you left off: https://getcamino.app/interview",
}
`;

exports[`email templates render exactly (localization guard) > weekly roundup 1`] = `
{
  "html": "<!doctype html>
<html><body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#FBFAF7;">
<div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;color:#15243B;">
  <div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:24px;">Get Camino <span style="color:#8A9BB0;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;">— your road to Spain</span></div>
  <p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">Hola — here’s where your road to Spain stands this week.</p><div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:#C0392B;margin:24px 0 12px;">SLIPPED PAST</div><div style="margin:0 0 18px;padding:14px 16px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E8E4DC;border-radius:10px;">
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;line-height:22px;"><span style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#C0392B;background:#FBEFED;border:1px solid #C0392B;border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;">OVERDUE</span> Register at your town hall (empadronamiento)</div>
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;margin-top:4px;"><span style="color:#C0392B;">was due 12 Jun</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="https://example.gob.es/empadronamiento" style="color:#2B5AA3;">official source ↗</a></div>
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;color:#4A5A70;margin-top:6px;">Book the cita previa now — appointment slots are the real bottleneck, not the paperwork.</div>
  </div><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;"><span style="font-size:13px;color:#4A5A70;">Already done one of these? Mark it done with the real date and your plan re-flows. Plans changed? Tell me what happened and I’ll remodel the roadmap.</span></p><div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:#BD8318;margin:24px 0 12px;">COMING UP</div><div style="margin:0 0 18px;padding:14px 16px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E8E4DC;border-radius:10px;">
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;line-height:22px;">Get your NIE (foreigner identification number)</div>
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;margin-top:4px;"><span style="color:#8A9BB0;">due 28 Jul</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="https://example.gob.es/nie" style="color:#2B5AA3;">official source ↗</a></div>
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;color:#4A5A70;margin-top:6px;">Book the cita previa now — appointment slots are the real bottleneck, not the paperwork.</div>
  </div><div style="margin:0 0 18px;padding:14px 16px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E8E4DC;border-radius:10px;">
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;line-height:22px;">Declare foreign assets (Modelo 720)</div>
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;margin-top:4px;"><span style="color:#8A9BB0;">due 30 Jul</span></div>
    <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;color:#4A5A70;margin-top:6px;">If in doubt, a gestor can prepare this in a day — cheap insurance against a mis-filing.</div>
  </div><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;"><span style="color:#8A9BB0;">…and 2 more after these — one step at a time.</span></p><div style="margin:24px 0;"><a href="https://getcamino.app/plan" style="display:inline-block;background:#2B5AA3;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:12px 22px;border-radius:8px;">Open your full roadmap</a></div>
  <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #E8E4DC;margin:32px 0 16px;">
  <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#8A9BB0;">
    You’re getting this because you have a Get Camino roadmap. <a href="https://getcamino.app/api/email/unsubscribe?uid=fixed&sig=fixed" style="color:#8A9BB0;">Unsubscribe from the weekly roundup</a>.
    <br>Guidance only — not legal or tax advice.
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>",
  "subject": "Your Get Camino week: 1 overdue, 2 coming up",
  "text": "Hola — here’s where your road to Spain stands this week.
[OVERDUE] Register at your town hall (empadronamiento) — was due 12 Jun
  official source: https://example.gob.es/empadronamiento
  tip: Book the cita previa now — appointment slots are the real bottleneck, not the paperwork.
Get your NIE (foreigner identification number) — due 28 Jul
  official source: https://example.gob.es/nie
  tip: Book the cita previa now — appointment slots are the real bottleneck, not the paperwork.
Declare foreign assets (Modelo 720) — due 30 Jul
  tip: If in doubt, a gestor can prepare this in a day — cheap insurance against a mis-filing.
…and 2 more after these.
Open your full roadmap: https://getcamino.app/plan",
}
`;

exports[`email templates render exactly (localization guard) > welcome 1`] = `
{
  "html": "<!doctype html>
<html><body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#FBFAF7;">
<div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;color:#15243B;">
  <div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:24px;">Get Camino <span style="color:#8A9BB0;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;">— your road to Spain</span></div>
  <p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">Hola — I’m Lola.</p><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">Get Camino turns your move to Spain into a step-by-step roadmap: every visa, form and deadline that applies to <em>your</em> situation, in the right order, each one backed by an official source.</p><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">Your roadmap lives here — it updates as your plans change, and I’ll coach you through any step you tap:</p><div style="margin:24px 0;"><a href="https://getcamino.app/plan" style="display:inline-block;background:#2B5AA3;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:12px 22px;border-radius:8px;">Open your roadmap</a></div><p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px;">While your move is underway I’ll send a short weekly roundup — what’s coming up, what’s slipped, never more than a handful of tasks.</p>
  <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #E8E4DC;margin:32px 0 16px;">
  <div style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#8A9BB0;">
    You’re getting this because you have a Get Camino roadmap. <a href="https://getcamino.app/api/email/unsubscribe?uid=fixed&sig=fixed" style="color:#8A9BB0;">Unsubscribe from the weekly roundup</a>.
    <br>Guidance only — not legal or tax advice.
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>",
  "subject": "Welcome to Get Camino — your road to Spain starts here",
  "text": "Hola — I’m Lola.

Get Camino turns your move to Spain into a step-by-step roadmap: every visa, form and deadline that applies to your situation, in the right order, backed by official sources.

Open your roadmap: https://getcamino.app/plan

While your move is underway I’ll send a short weekly roundup — never more than a handful of tasks.",
}
`;

